            <h2>What are cookies?</h2>
            <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They allow the site to recognize your device in future visits and remember your preferences.</p>

            <h2>Cookies we use</h2>

            <h3>Essential Cookies</h3>
